data.description: Charming 4 bed 3 bath home w/ gated courtyard entry! Light & bright interior featuring tile flooring, skylights, and spacious living & family rooms excellent for relaxation and entertaining. Spacious formal dining space flows to breakfast nook & kitchen complet with granite tile counters, tile backsplash, plenty of cabinets space, built-in appliances, NEW tile flooring, and French doors leading to the back patio. Continue onto the sizable primary bedroom to find a private bathroom with dual sinks. Generously sized secondary bedrooms & 2 additional full baths. NEW A/C! Expansive paver backyard and detached bonus room + storage shed w/ laundry hook ups.
